snippet.title: Wizardry The Five Ordeals English Language Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Wizardry The Five Ordeals received an English translation, which was shadow dropped during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022. Wizardry The Five Ordeals English language version is available now on Steam.
